This paper deals with the construction of frequency hopping sequence sets, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also involves the use of finite fields, which is a common topic in cryptography (cs.CR) and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper presents a new construction method, which could be of interest to researchers in signal processing (cs.SI) and networking (cs.NI).
